OL,3,CPolice officers sacked after leaving
OL,4,Cvulnerable man to die
OL,6,FTwo police officers have lost their
OL,7,Fjobs after being found guilty of gross
OL,8,Fmisconduct for leaving a vulnerable
OL,9,Fman to die outside a railway station
OL,10,Fin Cornwall.
OL,12,FA police disciplinary panel heard the
OL,13,Fvictim, 51, was drunk and vulnerable
OL,14,Fwhen they saw him outside St Erth
OL,15,Frailway station at 1am on a November
OL,16,Fmorning in 2022.
