OL,3,CPolice officers sacked after leaving
OL,4,Cvulnerable man to die
OL,6,FThe officers, PC David Bishop and
OL,7,Fformer PC Daniel Baber, asked for an
OL,8,Fambulance but left him after 50
OL,9,Fminutes as they went to another high
OL,10,Frisk incident. The man was not under
OL,11,Fany shelter and the weather conditions
OL,12,Fwere poor.
OL,14,FCCTV showed the pair drive by at
OL,15,F2:20am but they did not stop to check
OL,16,Fon the man. They returned again at 5am
OL,17,Fand found the rain soaked man still
OL,18,Fasleep.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
