OL,3,CPolice officers sacked after leaving
OL,4,Cvulnerable man to die
OL,6,FThe panel heard they asked for an
OL,7,Fambulance but stayed in their police
OL,8,Fcar a few feet away but close enough
OL,9,Fto hear him snoring, but 50 minutes
OL,10,Flater his condition deteriorated and
OL,11,Fhe later died in hospital.
OL,13,FThe disciplinary hearing was told the
OL,14,Fman died from drug intoxication and
OL,15,Fpneumonia and there were no claims
OL,16,Fthat the officers' inaction caused his
OL,17,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
