OL,3,CPolice officers sacked after leaving
OL,4,Cvulnerable man to die
OL,6,FPC Bishop made misleading entries on
OL,7,Fthe police log to overstate their
OL,8,Factions in monitoring the man's
OL,9,Fwelfare.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct said their safeguarding
OL,13,Factions 'were sorely lacking' and they
OL,14,Fdid not try to move him into a
OL,15,Fsheltered position or cover him to
OL,16,Fkeep warm on a cold night or drive him
OL,17,Fto hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
